        * include/makeinclude/rules.local.GNU:
          Reverted the $(PWD) changed, it caused unexpected problems. We are
          working on a better solution.

Thu Apr 15 12:33:27 UTC 2004  Johnny Willemsen  <jwillemsen@remedy.nl>

