          that needs to be performed regardless of the ACE_NDEBUG setting.

Thu Jan 22 13:25:49 2004  Chad Elliott  <elliott_c@ociweb.com>

        * ace/config-sunos5.5.h:
        * ace/config-sunos5.7.h:

